channel.title: GoBabyGo Louisville
channel.description: GoBabyGo Louisville, associated with the Doctor of Physical Therapy Program at Bellarmine University, has been building for four years and is excited to continue. Our next build is in March of 2018. Please contact Dr Beth Ennis at eennis@bellarmine.edu for information. Our students and community members of therapists, electricians, and other volunteers are excited to continue this project!
